{
  "stem": "18186.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The lady, my cousin's-- I said that my mother's cousin who jumped.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She went daylight, in daylight, to beg for food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were-- and they corrupted her, and that killed her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she was in her early 30s.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No idea.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- I don't know if that's about-- it was kilometers-- I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a little far.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We walked all day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We met four kids in-- in Wirke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were hiding in the-- a part of in the forest that was--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wirke, the town of the-- that was the town that we-- actually the forest that we--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we met them, and they wanted to-- we and [INAUDIBLE], and we were all like teaming up together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then rumors were going around in town, in Wirke, that there are four Jewish kids hiding.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were after us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow, by moving from every day to different areas, they couldn't-- they didn't caught up with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that day, when we met that-- the four other boys from a difference town, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were sitting together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to them, you know what?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's not a good idea to sit together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I know they know there-- there's four kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where were you sitting?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where was this?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where were you located?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the forest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they separated, and we all-- like not too far.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they caught them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden we hear walking steps, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- you-- in the forest you hear, if somebody walks, you hear walking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we took a peek, like behind the-- in between the-- the bushes.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
